title: Fri Post Show (11-5-21)
itunes:title: Fri Post Show (11-5-21)
description:
Bobby starts the show by running through his stack of stories that he didn’t get to during the week. Bobby talks about a new singing show where you can bet on contestants. Bobby talks more about the producer’s dinner last night. He also gets an update from Raymundo’s trip to the Soul Train Awards.
